```

Regularly, if new users have voted in polls available to the user, they will receive an [updateMessagePoll](https://core.telegram.org/constructor/updateMessagePoll), with updated [pollResults](https://core.telegram.org/constructor/pollResults).

The same constructor can also be fetched manually using [messages.getPollResults](https://core.telegram.org/method/messages.getPollResults).

