The collectible must be visible to the current user, for example it can be a Fragment user/phone number collectible we own, or a Fragment username that another user has enabled on their account, or another user's Fragment phone number that we can see thanks to the owner's [privacy settings](https://core.telegram.org/api/privacy).

# Business

Users can turn their Telegram account into a **business account**, gaining access to business features such as opening hours, location, quick replies, automated messages, custom start pages, chatbot support, and more.

For the moment, all Telegram Business features are available for free to [Premium](https://core.telegram.org/api/premium) subscribers.

### [](#opening-hours)Opening hours

```
