Since Telegram Business is currently included with the [Telegram Premium](https://core.telegram.org/api/premium) subscription, and Telegram Premium subscribers do not see [sponsored messages in channels](https://core.telegram.org/api/sponsored-messages).

This may be problematic for business owners that may want to launch and view their own Telegram ads via the [Telegram ad platform »](https://ads.telegram.org/).

